# Supabase Configuration (Required)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url_here
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here
VITE_SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_supabase_service_role_key_here

# Clerk Authentication (Required)
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=your_clerk_publishable_key_here

# News APIs (Optional - Hybrid System)
# Leave empty to use free Google News RSS
# Add any one (or all) to upgrade news quality

# NewsAPI.org - Best coverage, production-grade
# Free: 100 requests/day (dev only)
# Paid: $449/month (unlimited)
# Sign up: https://newsapi.org/
VITE_NEWSAPI_KEY=

# GNews API - Best value for money
# Free: 100 requests/day
# Paid: $9.99/month (10,000 requests)
# Sign up: https://gnews.io/
VITE_GNEWS_KEY=

# Currents API - Best free tier
# Free: 600 requests/day
# Paid: $12/month (10,000 requests)
# Sign up: https://currentsapi.services/
VITE_CURRENTS_KEY=

# ============================================
# HOW THE HYBRID NEWS SYSTEM WORKS:
# ============================================
# 
# 1. If NO API keys configured:
#    → Uses Google News RSS (free, unlimited)
#    → Works for all countries automatically
#    → Good quality news
#
# 2. If ANY API key configured:
#    → Tries APIs first (priority: NewsAPI > GNews > Currents)
#    → Falls back to RSS if API fails
#    → Best quality + reliability
#
# 3. You can add API keys later:
#    → No code changes needed
#    → System automatically uses them
#    → Instant quality upgrade
#
# ============================================
# RECOMMENDATION:
# ============================================
# 
# Start: Leave all API keys empty (use free RSS)
# Later: Add GNews key ($10/mo) for better quality
# Scale: Upgrade to NewsAPI ($449/mo) for production
#
